<div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><p>The <strong>CADmeister 2024 Version Up Seminar</strong> was successfully held on <strong>21st May 2025</strong> at <strong>Novotel Bangkok Bangna Hotel</strong>, with more than <strong>30 attendees</strong> joining the event.</p><p>The seminar covered a variety of insightful topics, including:</p><ul><li><p><strong>CAD Function Introduction</strong></p><p>- Boost efficiency by removing unnecessary tasks and improving functionality.</p><p>- Quickly generate model data and reflect design intent.</p><p>- Improve 3D verification and communication with better integration and visibility.</p></li><li><p><strong>PRESS Function Introduction</strong></p><p>- Strengthening efforts to enhance the initial design review process.</p><p>– Improving convenient design support functions, considering system diversification.</p><p>- The third is implementing automation mechanisms utilizing excel integration.</p></li><li><p><strong>MOLD Function Introduction</strong></p><p>- Enhancement of initial studies and modeling tasks</p><p>- Improvement of Mold concept design function</p><p>- BOM function</p></li><li><p><strong>CAM Function Introduction</strong></p><p>- Addition of new features in CAMX (new machining types) and improvements (additional parameters)</p><p>- Enhancement of on-machine measurement with CAM-MEASURE</p><p>- Enhancement of 3D profile functionality (support for arbitrary steel shapes)</p><p>- Enhancement of CAM-STRUCTURE</p><p>- Introduction of Electrode CAM</p></li><li><p><strong>Useful Knowledge Sharing</strong><br>- Introduce some handy features you might find useful in your daily work.<br> </p></li></ul><p>Participants gained valuable insights into the new features and practical applications of CADmeister 2024 through live demonstrations and expert presentations.</p></div></div></div></div></div><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p></div>